column1: Maisí is a municipality and town in the Guantánamo Province of Cuba. Its administrative seat is located in the town of La Máquina.

column2: Punta Maisí (called "Baitiquiri" by the Taino in pre-colonial times) is located in this municipality.
the municipality of Maisí had a population of 28

column4: it has a population density of 53.9/km2 (140/sq mi).
